1203
01:09:26.485 --> 01:09:30.405
states. And these cell states recapitulate many patterns

1204
01:09:30.464 --> 01:09:34.054
from development of the brain. So some of the cells, one

1205
01:09:34.224 --> 01:09:37.964
state resembles neural progenitors, another resembles

1206
01:09:37.985 --> 01:09:41.204
oligodendrocytes progenitors, a third state

1207
01:09:41.584 --> 01:09:45.485
resembles astrocytes as well as their progenitors, and finally, we

